\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "It's a long way round, isn't it?" he queried.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "We aren't going round," replied Theon. "I want to get
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 to the top before nightfall."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Alvin said nothing. He had been rathe\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 r afraid of this.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 FROM HERE, SAID THEON, RAISING HIS VOICE TO MAKE IT
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 heard above the thunder of the waterfall, "you can see the
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 whole of Lys."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Alvin could well believe him. To the north lay mile upon
