\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Theon answered his fri\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 end's unspoken question.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "Once the whole of Lys was inhabited," he said, "but that
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 was a very long time ago. Only the animals live here now."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Indeed, there was nowhere any sign of human life\hich\f39 \emdash \loch\f39 none
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 of the clearings or well-disciplined rivers that spoke of Ma\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 n's
