\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 THE CRATER DWELLER
\par \page \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 IT WAS NIG\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 HT WHEN ALVIN AWOKE, THE UTTER NIGHT OF
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 mountain country, terrifying in its intensity. Something had
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 disturbed him, some whisper of sound that had crept into
