\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "That must be Shalmirane," he said simply.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "Shalmirane! Does it still exist?"
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "I'd almost forgotten," replied Theon, "but it's coming
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 back now. Mother once told me that the fortress lies in those
