\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Shalmirane! To these children of two races, so widely differing
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 in culture and history, this was\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39  indeed a name of magic.
