\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 The Battle of Shalmirane lay at the dawn of recorded history:
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 it marked the end of the le\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 gendary ages of Man's conquests,
