\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 accusation.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "We have no desire to keep you here in Lys against your
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 will, but you must surely realize what it would mean if our
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 people mixed. Between our culture and yours is a gulf as
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 great as any that ever separated Earth from its ancient
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 colonies. Think of this one fact, Alvin. You and Theon are
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 now of nearly the same age--but he and I will have been
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 dead for centuries when you are stiJJ a boy."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 The room was very quiet, so quiet that Alvin could hear
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 the strange, plaintive cries of unknown beasts in the Selds
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 beyond the village. Presently he said, almost in a whisper:
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "What do you want me to do?"
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "I have put your case to the Council, as I promised\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 , but
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 the law cannot be altered. You may remain here and become
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 one of us, or you may return to Diaspar. If you do that, we
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 \hich\f39 must \'a3\loch\f39 rst reshape the patterns of your mind so that you
\par \page \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 AGAINST THE FALL OF NIGHT 83
