\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 us."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "And Rorden? He would still know the truth, even if I
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 had forgotten everything."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "We have spoken with Rorden many times since you left.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 He recognizes the wisdom of our actions."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 In that dark moment, it seemed to Alvin that the whole wor\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 ld had turned against him. Though there was much truth
