\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Alvin waited until his racing thoughts were once more
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 under control.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "Theon," he began, "you'll help me, won't you?"
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 The other nodded but did not speak.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "Then tell me this--how could your people stop me if
