\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "I see. Can you tell if she is watching my mind now?"
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Theon looked worried, but his protest answered the question.
\par 
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "I shouldn't tell you that!"
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "But you will, won't you?"
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 The two bOys looked silently \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 at each other for many
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 seconds. Then Theon smiled.
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "You can't bully me, you know. Whatever you're planning
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 --and / can't read your mind--as soon as you tried to put
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 it into action Mother would take over. She won't let you
