\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 except these two disappeared. The one on the right is the
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 original."
\par \page \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 ALVIN WAS STILL STUNNED, BUT SLOWLY HE BEGAN TO KEALize
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 what must have happened. His robot could not be forced
