\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 and so were most of the visitors. Rorden himself was not as
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 terriSed as he had expected: his fears were still there, but he
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 had faced them at last. Something of Alvin's own reckless- ness--or was it courage?--had changed his outl\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 ook and given
