\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 things without question, and this is one of them. But my
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 machines know nothing of legend, only of truth--and there
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 is no historical record of such an agreement. I am convinced
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 that anything so important would have b\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 een permanently
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 recorded, as many lesser matters have been."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Alvin, he thought, would have been proud of him now.
