\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "I am Vanamonde."
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 There came a pause (how long the pattern o\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 f their thoughts
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 took to form!) and then the question was repeated. They had
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 not understood: that was strange, for surely their kind had
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 given him his name for it to be among the memories of his
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 birth. Those memories were very few, and they began
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 strangely\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39  at a single point in time, but they were crystal-clear,
