\par 
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "Who were the Great Ones--arc you one of them yourself?"
\par 
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 He did not know: they could scarcely believe him, and
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 their disappointment came sharp and clear across the abyss
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 separating their minds from his. But they were patient and
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 he was glad to help them, for their quest was the same as his
