\par \page \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 142\tab AGAINST TH\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 E FALL OF NIGHT
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 As long as he lived, Alvin did not believe he would ever
