\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 hims\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 elf, that Theon's mind was so much more powerful than
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 his own. He could only wait and wonder, half dazed by the
