\par 
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 Presently Theon, rather pale and strained, broke off the
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 contact and turned to \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 his friend.
