\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 "it's mind may be of such a different order that we can't
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 understand it--\hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 yet somehow I don't believe that is the right
\par \hich\af39\dbch\af31505\loch\f39 explanation."
